snippet.title: Sanguivore: Twenty Below - Teaser 2023
snippet.description: Survive and strategize with friends in Sanguivore, a first-person escape-room style nightmare. Your mission: lead your team to safety through one of multiple escape routes, while evading bloodthirsty monsters hunting you. Work together to survive.
